      "text": "| Tool               | InFlightSummary | InFlightPreview | InFlightDetail | CompletedSummary | CompletedPreview | CompletedDetail |\n| ------------------ | :-------------: | :-------------: | :------------: | :--------------: | :--------------: | :-------------: |\n| getFile            |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |       ✅        |\n| hover              |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n| findReferences     |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n| diagnostics        |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n| bashCommand        |       ✅        |       ✅        |       ✅       |        ✅        |        ✅        |       ✅        |\n| thread-title       |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n| spawn-subagent     |       ✅        |       ✅        |       —        |        ✅        |        ✅        |       ✅        |\n| spawn-foreach      |       ✅        |       ✅        |       —        |        ✅        |        ✅        |       ✅        |\n| wait-for-subagents |       ✅        |       ✅        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n| yield-to-parent    |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n| edl                |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        ✅        |       ✅        |\n| mcp/tool           |       ✅        |        —        |       —        |        ✅        |        —         |        —        |\n\n## Progress types to move\n\nSome tools export Progress types used only in rendering. These should move to the render file:",
